   version stable 4.9.5 4.9.4 4.9.2
   require phonon dbus-python libGLU qt-everywhere-opensource sip
  category development
 attribute library makej multilib-dual python-module
    source $SOURCEFORGE_URL pyqt/PyQt4/PyQt-$VERSION/PyQt-x11-gpl-$VERSION.tar.gz
#   source http://www.riverbankcomputing.co.uk/static/Downloads/PyQt4/PyQt-x11-gpl-$VERSION.tar.gz
      info last 20120930
      info home http://www.riverbankcomputing.co.uk/software/pyqt
      info vurl http://www.riverbankcomputing.co.uk/software/pyqt/download
      desc 'set of Python bindings for Nokias Qt 
application framework and runs on all platforms supported by Qt 
including Windows, MacOS/X and Linux.
There are two sets of bindings:
PyQt v4 supports Qt v4;
and the older PyQt v3 supports Qt v3 and earlier.
The bindings are implemented as a set of Python modules 
and contain over 300 classes and over 6,000 functions and methods.'

build(){
 echo 'yes' |
 python configure.py &&
 make &&
 make install DESTDIR=$DESTDIR
}


current(){
case $VERSION in
 4.7.4) grep -qx /usr/bin/pyuic4 $INSTALL_LOGS/PyQt4 ;;
esac
}
